	('983d6c7e-c45b-4837-b9bd-c5e1a737d94c', 'Generative AI', 'generative-ai-bsc11326', NULL, 'BSC11326', 'course', 'college', 'BSc-Level', 'This course provides a foundational understanding of Generative Artificial Intelligence, focusing on how machines can create new content such as text, images, audio, and code. Learners will explore key GenAI models, including neural networks, transformers, and diffusion models, while discovering real-world applications across industries. No prior AI experience required.', 'Generative AI is an intermediate program designed for school students looking to build strong expertise in science knowledge and applied learning. This course provides a foundational understanding of Generative Artificial Intelligence, focusing on how machines can create new content such as text, images, audio, and code. Learners will explore key GenAI models, including neural networks, transformers, and diffusion models, while discovering real-world applications across industries. No prior AI experience required. This course provides a structured learning path that blends theoretical foundations with practical application, ensuring learners gain real-world readiness. By the end of this program, participants will be able to explain fundamental concepts behind generative ai models, understand how neural networks learn patterns and generate data. With a duration of 8 weeks, this program is carefully paced to deliver maximum learning outcomes through engaging content, hands-on exercises, and expert guidance.', 320, 'Online', 'Intermediate', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0.00, 'INR', '[]', '["Explain fundamental concepts behind generative AI models", "Understand how neural networks learn patterns and generate data", "Recognize the role of large language models (LLMs)"]', '["School students looking to build foundational knowledge", "Students preparing for competitive examinations", "Learners seeking to explore new subject areas"]', '["Explain fundamental concepts behind generative AI models", "Understand how neural networks learn patterns and generate data", "Recognize the role of large language models (LLMs)", "Describe how AI can generate images, text, and multimedia"]', '[]', '[]', NULL, NULL, NULL, false, true, 8, '2026-02-23 04:48:17.033578+00', '2026-02-23 04:48:17.033578+00'),
